<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
	<p><%= @player.name %>球友您好,</p>
	<p>這是您報名參加的桌球愛好者聯盟<%=@gamename%> 出賽提醒通知郵件。</p>
	<p>
  	提醒您,您報名的本項賽事將於 <strong><font color='red'><%= @holdgame.startdate.to_s %></font></strong>舉行,請準時出席.<br>若您不克參賽,請儘速前往報名網頁取消報名,以利賽事安排！<br>
    <strong><font color='red'>如果無故缺賽,將可能被主辦人列入黑名單,爾後無法再報名該主辦人所舉辦的桌盟賽事,敬請配合！</font></strong>  
	</p>
  <p>分組開賽時間提醒</p>

    <table border=1 align=center>
      <tr>
        <th align=center>組別</th>
        <th align=center>開賽時間</th>
      </tr>
      <% @holdgame.gamegroups.each_with_index do |gamegroup| %>
      <tr>

         <td align=left><font color=blue>  <%= gamegroup.groupname %></font></td>  
         <td align=left><font color=red>  <strong><%= gamegroup.starttime.strftime("%F %H:%M")  %></strong></font></td>  
      </tr> 
      <%end%> 
    </table>
 

  </p>  
	<p>桌球愛好者聯盟敬上</p>
  <p>請勿直接回覆本郵件！</p>
  <p>如果有任何問題請跟本賽事主辦人：<%=@holdgame.gameholder.name%> 連絡. <br>
     連絡電話：<%=@holdgame.gameholder.phone %> <br>
     email: <%= mail_to @holdgame.gameholder.email, @holdgame.gameholder.email %><br>
   </p>   
 	<%= link_to  @holdgame.startdate.to_s+@holdgame.gamename+'報名網頁', holdgame_gamegroups_url(@holdgame) %>
  </body>
</html>